  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the safety, efficacy and concentration of nilotinib over time in the Ph+ chronic
      myelogenous leukemia (CML) in pediatric patients (from 1 to &lt;18 years).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
